*Declare a date type.

REPORT Z_ABAP101_004.

*We can declare a date type using the 'DATS' data type.

DATA lv_date TYPE DATS.

*This line declares variable named 'lv_date' of type 'DATS',
*which is used to store date values in ABAP.
*or

TYPES creation_date TYPE d.

*We can use these variable to handle date-related information within our ABAP programs.